Text:
Not the up-loaders' fault, but this is bad. 

She says in the interview in the beginning that she's only doing this for the money, and during the session it clearly shows that she's not enjoying it at all but only wants to get it over with. It doesn't help that the camera guy asks her to do stuff she doesn't appreciate.

Nice looking girl, but out of her element, as is the director/cameraman. Very annoying to listen to his constant comments.
Don't listen to him. Great girl, great body, great scenes.
